{"tid":1946902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"廿蚊張要求政府協助飲食界支付14天租金、工資及寬免差餉 呼籲業主繼續減租","createTime":"2020-03-28T02:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T03:56:54.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b835acad5b4ba31066ca723018ab2a6ac4fc326b","tid":1946902,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:41:29.000Z","msg":"身兼行政會議成員的飲食界立法會議員張宇人表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">會要求政府能向財委會申請撥款，為受新防疫措施影響的飲食業界支付14天的租金和工資，以及寬減、甚至寬免一季差餉等</span>，協助飲食業界渡過難關。<br />\n<br />\n張宇人表示，受疫情影響，過去幾個月飲食業界只有於3月初時，生意額稍有回升，2月和4月的情況困難，加上昨日政府宣布針對食肆的新防疫措施，對業界造成很大衝擊，<span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲早前願意減租的業主，4月份繼續減租，期望未有減租的業主，4月份能減租，顧全大局</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外，稻苗學會主席徐汶緯出席一個電台節目表示，全港有1萬3千個飲食牌照可提供堂食，如果疫情令當中1成食肆要倒閉，可能會造成大批飲食業界員工失業。<br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的現代飲食專業管理協會主席梁志偉認為，在新防疫政策下，業界會有犧牲，但基於社會責任，業界願意盡量配合，與社會共度難關<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517384-20200328.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517384-20200328.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=f6d8b8b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517384-20200328.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=490a35c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517384-20200328.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"90869d90f87c2d97df150881718a72037c41424a","tid":1946902,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6a8e8ed2e4bdb79a46d2f3b219fb50f6295b2f","tid":1946902,"uid":166733,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:43:20.000Z","msg":"香港做生意包賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe62f6a06148626b26d98410e18853d6b5d798bd","tid":1946902,"uid":85358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:43:54.000Z","msg":"如果可以政府比錢, 我相信9成零售主動想唔開工, 好過日日無生意"},{"pid":"d3dc3b407a3c3e57ad9985cbc952763327167caa","tid":1946902,"uid":117344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:44:18.000Z","msg":"不如一齊玩 #黃店外賣challenge #yellowshopchallenge?<br />\n<br />\n咁鍾意ig story tag人 不如整個#黃店外賣challengeaccepted?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1945867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1945867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e06781a5ac085163b62ac3b36ef599ab00ade703","tid":1946902,"uid":3513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"講到底又係要錢 俾你開門都唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1283121d1b9a06cc7d6fca597935c034520bf52","tid":1946902,"uid":297997,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:46:21.000Z","msg":"On9<br />\n<br />\n你減租唔撚得<br />\n<br />\n交稅幫你交租"},{"pid":"3e23097e48f2492da2b9ca74623918039a2b2385","tid":1946902,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7598e156cad75daa1482dea4ddc08d34648ca9","tid":1946902,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:48:28.000Z","msg":"執笠囉"},{"pid":"1e4245552fa0c0e6ac34d56e31941d1867bb4a1d","tid":1946902,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a751c721d23a90029e147af49b3c3664d5a283","tid":1946902,"uid":251433,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T02:50: